Name: shoginn-flightaware
Overview:
FlightAware is a digital aviation company that operates a flight tracking and data platform. This docker contains the binary for FlightAware's FlightFeeder application, which consumes an ADSB feed and uploads the parsed data to FA.[br][br]
        Refer to the support thread for instructions on how to setup a dump1090 feed with your radio device.[br][br]
